alfresco clustering

1) make sure that nfs share point reachable
2) run docker-container with --privileged for mounting nfs
3) change root directory option in option-file which used in auto-installation of alfresco (prifix option in option-file)
4) change the share point and mount path in dockerfile
5) give same database path & all db info in all alfresco server ( in option-file ) 


